yle=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|'''[[1920 United States presidential election|1920]]'''\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|22.1% ''104''\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|'''73.6%''' ''346''\n|  style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|4.3% ''20''\n|-\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|'''[[1916 United States presidential election|1916]]'''\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|4.3% ''14''\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|'''95.1%''' ''311''\n|  style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|0.6% ''2''\n|-\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|'''[[1912 United States presidential election|1912]]'''\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Republican}}|0.4% ''1''\n|  style=\"text-align:center;\" {{Party shading/Democratic}}|'''63.4%''' ''159''\n|  style=\"text-align:center; background:honeyDew;\"|36.3% ''91''\n|}\n{{Hidden end}}\n\n==Education==\nWest Carroll Parish [[Public school (government funded)|public schools]] are operated by the [[West Carroll Parish School Board]]. The public school system consist of four high schools and five elementary schools that consistently rank at the top of the state in test scores and on the athletic field.\n\n==National Guard==\nThe 921ST Engineer Company (Vertical) of the [[528th Engineer Brigade]] resides in [[Oak Grove, West Carroll Parish, Louisiana|Oak Grove, Louisiana]].\n\n==Communities==\n[[Image:Map of West Carroll Parish Louisiana With Municipal Labels.PNG|thumb|200px|Map of West Carroll Parish, Louisiana With Municipal Labels]]\n\n===Towns===\n* [[Oak Grove, West Carroll Parish, Louisiana|Oak Grove]] (parish seat)\n\n===Villages===\n* [[Epps, Louisiana|Epps]]\n* [[Forest, Louisiana|Forest]]\n* [[Kilbourne, Louisiana|Kilbourne]]\n* [[Pioneer, Louisiana|Pioneer]]\n\n===Unincorporated communities===\n* Goodwill\n\n==Prison=